        "make sure to click on the modelname and to select the microsoft/Trellis.2-B \n\nin case you encounter following error message: \nRepo id must use alphanumeric chars, '-', '_' or '.'. The name cannot start or end with '-' or '.' and the maximum length is 96: 'E:\\ComfyUI-Easy-Install\\ComfyUI-Easy-Install\\ComfyUI\\models\\microsoft\\TRELLIS.2-4B/ckpts'\n\nHere is the updated script that resolves the issue by downloading all 20 required files directly into ComfyUI\\models\\microsoft\\TRELLIS.2-4B.\nBefore running the script, make sure to delete the existing ComfyUI\\models\\microsoft folder.\nThen run the script from either the ComfyUI root directory or the Add-ons directory.\n\nYou can [download it here](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Mj7pWL3FuF8_eToyV-9cXsByV_XRpdhf?usp=sharing)"
